22:
this is the word that Yahweh has spoken about him:\q1 "The virgin daughter of Zion despises you and laughs you to scorn;
\q1 the daughter of Jerusalem shakes her head at you.
\q1

29:
Because of your raging against me, and because your arrogance has reached my ears,\q1 I will put my hook in your nose, and my bit in your mouth;
\q1 I will turn you back the way you came."


